課程概述 Course Description
       本課程以一系列專題討論，深入淺出的講授工程力學應用在土木工程領域方面的相關課題。講授內容著重在說明問題之背景、理論基礎、以及數學模式之解析方法與應用等，旨在增進研究生之研究與論文寫作能力。 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
Vector and Tensor AnalysisGeneralized Plane problem for a Body with AnisotropyStroh Formalism and general solutions for inplane and antiplane deformationsSome Elastodynamic TheorySpecial mathematical functions 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1General equations of the theory of anisotropic elasticity2General equations and statement of the basic anisotropic problems3Examples of simple anisotropic materials: elongation of a rod under the action4Examples of simple anisotropic materials: The bending of a rod by moments applied to the ends5General case of distribution of stresses which depend on only two coordinates6General expressions for the stress functions, general formulas for the components of stresses and displacement and the boundary conditions7Generalized plane deformation in a homogeneous anisotropic bodycomponents of stresses and displacement and the boundary conditions8Plane deformation and the state of generalized plane stress9Examples of generalized plane problems10The problem of plane deformation of a body with cylindrical anisotropy11Generalized torsion and the torsion of a rod possessing cylindrical anisotropy12Torsion of a shaft with variable moduli of elasticity13Bending of an orthotropic cantilever with a rectangular cross section14The approximate methods of the solution of the problem of the bending of a cantilever.15The deformations of solids of revolution16Symmetric deformation,torsion of a conical rod17Tension and bending of in a conical rod18The distribution of stresses in a spherical shell container under pressure 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


