課程概述 Course Description
       本課程以一系列專題討論，深入淺出的講授工程力學應用在土木工程領域方面的相關課題。講授內容著重在說明問題之背景、理論基礎、以及數學模式之解析方法與應用等，旨在增進研究生之研究與論文寫作能力。 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
異向性彈性力學之Stroh理論架構介紹固體力學廣義平面問題之解析方法利用特殊函數求解異向性力學問題與探討 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Stroh Formalism:uncoupling of inplane and antiplane displacements2Stroh Formalism:Antiplane deformation3Stroh Formalism:general solutions for antiplane deformations4Stroh Formalism:Green’s functions, the sextic formalism of Stroh5Stroh Formalism:Green’s functions, the sextic formalism of Stroh6Generalized Plane problem: Rectilinearly Anisotropy7Generalized Plane problem: Rectilinearly Anisotropy8Generalized Plane problem: Cylindrical Anisotropy9Generalized Plane problem: Cylindrical Anisotropy10Generalized Plane problem:non-homogeneous rectilinearly orthotropic body11Generalized Plane problem:non-homogeneous rectilinearly orthotropic body12Generalized Plane problem: torsions of bars13Generalized Plane problem: torsions of bars14Some Elastodynamic Theory15Some Elastodynamic Theory16Some Elastodynamic Theory17Special Functions18Special Functions 

